and this one in particular

00:04:13.780 --> 00:04:17.970
since it is a special edition
of the Vardanants series.

00:04:17.970 --> 00:04:21.510
So, please, join me in
welcoming Dr. Mary Jane Deeb.

00:04:21.510 --> 00:04:31.590
[ Applause ]

00:04:31.590 --> 00:04:35.710
&gt;&gt; Thank You, LaVon, and
thank you Mark Sweeney,

00:04:35.710 --> 00:04:39.190
for all your support and
for everything you've done.

00:04:39.190 --> 00:04:42.560
So, honored guests, ladies
and gentlemen good morning.

00:04:42.560 --> 00:04:46.960
I too wish to welcome you
to the Library of Congress.

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:49.580
And in the name of the Division,

00:04:49.580 --> 00:04:51.530
the African Middle
East division,

00:04:51.530 --> 00:04:54.360
which is hosting
this program today.

