00:15:28.280 --> 00:15:30.490
because that's why I
prepared this program.

00:15:30.490 --> 00:15:34.310
While she is talking,
you may read it.

00:15:34.310 --> 00:15:36.160
The one thing I want
to draw your attention

00:15:36.160 --> 00:15:42.530
to about Dr. Evans is that she
is curating yet another exhibit,

00:15:42.530 --> 00:15:47.580
and this exhibit is on Armenia,
a huge exhibit on Armenian Art,

00:15:47.580 --> 00:15:49.720
which will open at the
Metropolitan Museum

00:15:49.720 --> 00:15:53.400
of Art on September 22nd.

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:58.320
So, at this point, Dr. Helen
Evans, to speak on Silesia

